Create: Add new key-value pairs to the database.
Read: Retrieve all key-value pairs from the database.
Update: Modify the value associated with a specific key in the database.
Delete: Remove a key-value pair from the database.

API Endpoints
GET /data/: Retrieve all key-value pairs from the database.
POST /data/: Add a new key-value pair to the database.
DELETE /data/<name>/: Delete the key-value pair with the specified name from the database.

